<h1>Naive Bayes Text Analyzer</h1>
<p>Based on two lexicons of positive and negative opinion words and
  'Rotten Tomatoes' movie reviews, the output will classify your input
  text as either positive or negative.</p>

<h3>Enter text to analyze</h3>
<form method="post" action="/result">
  <div>
    <textarea name="text_to_analyze" rows='5' cols='75'></textarea>
  </div>
  <div>
    <input type="submit" value="Analyze">
  </div>
</form>

